data.description: This charming 3-bedroom,2-bath home is a true gem in a historic neighborhood. The main level boasts recently renovated HW flooring, adding a touch of modern elegance to the classic design. the MBA was fully renovated in 2021, offering a luxurious and updated space. The den is a reader's dream with an entire wall of floor-to-ceiling bookshelves. New carpet and light from the French doors completest his cozy place. You will find stainless steel appliances and concrete countertops in the kitchen. The bedrooms are roomy with nice-sized closets and lots of natural light to make you feel right at home. The finished daylight BSM offers extra living space. The home received significant updates: Roof-2018 along with new windows anew HVAC in 2023.
